                                                        <Run FontSize="48" Foreground="DarkBlue">Steve Price</Run>
                                                        <LineBreak />
                                                        <LineBreak />

                                                        Steve Price is a legend of league on both sides of the Tasman and is recognised as one of the best role models and leaders in sport today.
