                                                        <Run FontSize="48" Foreground="DarkBlue">Our history</Run> <LineBreak /><LineBreak />  <Run Foreground="DarkMagenta"> We have been operating for over 30 years, read about how Child Cancer Foundation began.</Run><LineBreak /><LineBreak />
